2,17 Z M13.796012,15.7713945 C13.2202627,15.9222769 12.6169095,16 12,16 C8.65501663,16 6,13.7242715 6,11 C6,8.27572854 8.65501663,6 12,6 C15.3449834,6 18,8.27572854 18,11 C18,12.0842731 17.5831655,13.1194459 16.8141738,13.9796336 C16.416188,14.4248172 16.3323351,15.1207601 16.5018219,16.2746263 L16.539079,16.5115665 C15.2664214,15.853575 14.4145404,15.6093014 13.796012,15.7713945 Z"></path></svg></i></span><span class="Button__labelItem"> Comment</span></button></div></div><div class="SocialFooter__action" data-testid="overflow"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--transparent Button--small Button--rounded" aria-label="More options, Menu pop up"><span class="Button__labelItem"><i class="Icon MoreIcon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6,10 C7.1045695,10 8,10.8954305 8,12 C8,13.1045695 7.1045695,14 6,14 C4.8954305,14 4,13.1045695 4,12 C4,10.8954305 4.8954305,10 6,10 Z M12,10 C13.1045695,10 14,10.8954305 14,12 C14,13.1045695 13.1045695,14 12,14 C10.8954305,14 10,13.1045695 10,12 C10,10.8954305 10.8954305,10 12,10 Z M18,10 C19.1045695,10 20,10.8954305 20,12 C20,13.1045695 19.1045695,14 18,14 C16.8954305,14 16,13.1045695 16,12 C16,10.8954305 16.8954305,10 18,10 Z"></path></svg></i></span></button></div></div></div></footer></section></article><article class="ReviewCard" aria-label="Review by brian   "><div class="ReviewCard__profile"><div class="ReviewerProfile ReviewerProfile--medium"><section class="ReviewerProfile__avatar"><a class="Avatar Avatar--medium" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/193310-brian" as="div"><img data-testid="image" class="Avatar__image" alt="Profile Image for brian   ." src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1353195524i/193310._UX200_CR0,50,200,200_.jpg"/></a></section><section class="ReviewerProfile__info"><span class="Text Text__title4"><div data-testid="name" class="ReviewerProfile__name"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user