\u003e as I did for the texts I mentioned above though, for me, it was just too awful to read. The scenes held absolutely nothing back. I am not a person easily shocked or put off by such things, though it was too much even for me. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e \u003ci\u003eThe Republic of Wine\u003c/i\u003e is the only other book to make me feel this unnerved (because of baby cannibalism.) It made me want to vomit as the writing here did. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003ci\u003eThe Bluest Eye\u003c/i\u003e was \u003cu\u003eway\u003c/u\u003e too much for me. It was overly symbolic, melodramatically brutal and displayed no hope or optimism. I did not enjoy a single page.","rating":1,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/27788046?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"1-star-reads","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/27788046?shelf=1-star-reads"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"postcolonial","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/27788046?shelf=postcolonial"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"i-tried","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/27788046?shelf=i-tried"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2428863922"},"likeCount":138,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":25,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:43107057":{"id":43107057,"__typename":"User","legacyId":43107057,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1609358692i/43107057._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":204,"viewableName":"Read By RodKelly","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/43107057-read-by-rodkelly","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":704},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.q96b